      • withinRange

        public static <T extends MatchResult,S extends MatchType> com.google.common.base.Predicate<T> withinRange(S minMatchType,
                                                                                                          com.google.common.collect.BoundType minBound,
                                                                                                          S maxMatchType,
                                                                                                          com.google.common.collect.BoundType maxBound)
        Generates a Predicate that only accepts the Match Results within a range. The range may be closed or open at each of the boundaries. BoundType.CLOSED means that the boundary should also be accepted. BoundType.OPEN on the other indicates that the boundary itself should not be accepted.
        Type Parameters:
        T - a subclass of MatchResult
        S - a subclass of MatchType
        Parameters:
        minMatchType - the matchType that defines the lower boundary
        minBound - the lower BoundType
        maxMatchType - the matchType that defines the upper boundary
        maxBound - the upper BoundType
        Returns:
        the Predicate
